{"tid":2314870,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【環球時報：一堆廢鐵】美軍兩棲攻擊艦馬金島號進入南海","createTime":"2020-12-06T23:07:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:16:43.000Z","uid":54337,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"907fc049f51d1d53ccd165babdf8e5853eae9473","tid":2314870,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:07:15.000Z","msg":"中美南海角力持續 美軍兩棲艦隊現身<br />\n<br />\n美國加強在中國周邊的軍事部署，區內局勢持續緊張。中國北京大學海洋研究院南海戰略態勢感知計劃周日（6日）指，美軍一個兩棲戰備群當天進入南海。<br />\n南海戰略態勢感知計劃在社交網表示，美國海軍兩棲攻擊艦馬金島號與兩棲船塢運輸艦薩默塞特號，兵分兩路進入南海。根據航海路線圖，馬金島號經台灣南部與菲律賓北部之間的巴士海峽前往南海，薩默塞特號則取道菲律賓中部。<br />\n暫未知該兩棲戰備群之後的動向，包括會否在南海舉行演習，或針對中國在區內的島嶼執行航行自由行動。資料顯示，該兩棲戰備群還包括兩棲船塢運輸艦聖迭戈號及第15海軍陸戰遠征隊，馬金島號則具備操作F35B隱形戰機的能力。"},{"pid":"04ac162f351c0a7cc64febcfc1ace31334d9a76e","tid":2314870,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:07:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201206/mobile/bkn-20201206191953400-1206_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201206%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201206191953400-1206_00952_001.html&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2pMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=0b715924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201206/mobile/bkn-20201206191953400-1206_00952_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201206/photo/bkn-20201206191953400-1206_00952_001_01p.jpg?20201206195203\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201206%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20201206191953400-1206_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20201206195203&h=b4945de3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a1464bd3b063ebcdf9e76c0f6a2160f34e8dd9d5","tid":2314870,"uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T23:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8E9VA_vwPmNeaM0GGk6TPc9BN1w=/460x264/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/